<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-6754] DefaultCodec.createOutputStream() leaks memory</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-6754</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;DefaultCodec.createOutputStream() creates a new Compressor instance in each OutputStream. Even if the OutputStream is closed, this leaks memory.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12463934">HADOOP-6754</key>
            <summary>DefaultCodec.createOutputStream() leaks memory</summary>
